parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TIPM can cause the vehicle to stall or shut off while driving, leading to a loss of power steering and brakes, which can increase the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts off while driving
difficulty starting the vehicle
intermittent starting issues
battery drain
fuel pump failure
and electrical system malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected shut-off of the engine while driving can lead to a loss of control, increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The engine shuts off while driving
sometimes without warning
and may not restart immediately. The dashboard lights and accessories may also turn off
and the steering and brakes may become unresponsive.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wheel bearings can cause the vehicle to vibrate, lose control, or even lead to a wheel separation, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: Grinding noises from the wheel bearings
vibration while driving
and eventual failure of the wheel bearings.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Rack and Pinion Hydraulic Line Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rack and pinion hydraulic line can cause a loss of steering control, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: Cracking or failure of the hydraulic line
loss of steering control
and difficulty maneuvering the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden stalling or shut-off of the engine can cause loss of power steering, brakes, and other essential systems, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine shuts off without warning
power steering and brakes fail
the vehicle stalls while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to become stuck in gear, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission fails to engage
the vehicle will not shift into gear
the vehicle is stuck in limp mode.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine noise or ticking sound can indicate a more serious underlying issue, leading to engine failure or damage.
symptoms: A ticking sound comes from the engine
the engine fly-wheel is damaged
the engine head needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission jerking or harsh shifting can cause loss of control, leading to accidents or damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: The vehicle jerks or shifts harshly
the transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle has difficulty shifting into gear.
